<title>UK: LIFFE to list four new equity options.</title>
<headline>LIFFE to list four new equity options.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>The London International Financial Futures and Options Exchange (LIFFE) announced on Friday it intends to make available equity options on the shares of Gallaher Group, Halifax, Norwich Union and Woolwich.</p>
<p>Each option will be made available on the same day as when the company's shares commence trading and these dates are epected to be:</p>
<p>    Gallaher Group   -  Friday, May 30</p>
<p>    Halifax	    -  Monday, June 2</p>
<p>    Norwich Union    -  Monday, June 16</p>
<p>    Woolwich	   -  Monday, July 7</p>
<p>The inroduction of these new individual equity options will increase the number available at LIFFE to 75.</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 7954</p>
